{"tid":482201,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Android 新保安漏洞 近八成用戶受影響","createTime":"2017-11-28T03:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T15:07:45.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"29b16b19562a1db081618e891080b47feedea9c8","tid":482201,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T03:02:46.000Z","msg":"Android 這個系統平台，似乎每隔一段時間就爆出有保安漏洞的消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，如「C&amp;D」病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、藏有 Ztorg 木馬毒的 Android apps 等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。今次 Android 的新漏洞來自系統的「MediaProjection」功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，由於此服務的存取權限至《Android 5.0》以後，才開放給開發人員，預計今次受影響的 Android 用戶達 78.7%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！？<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1950000/1952372/20171121_Ming01_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1950000%2F1952372%2F20171121_Ming01_1024.jpg&h=e0cfee85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1952372/Android%20新保安漏洞%20%20近八成用戶受影響\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1952372%2FAndroid%2520%E6%96%B0%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%2520%2520%E8%BF%91%E5%85%AB%E6%88%90%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E5%8F%97%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF&d=2BKKJ%2BOImTxr1i6c42X8igRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=d348c113\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1952372/Android%20新保安漏洞%20%20近八成用戶受影響</a></div>"},{"pid":"e2ad5c843e7c6d907ce1958ca516dc0b47267fe4","tid":482201,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T03:04:52.000Z","msg":"Google 雖然不停推出新的《Android》系統，但能真正獲享最新版本系統的用戶並不多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，令不少《Android》用戶仍停留在舊版本的《Android》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1950000/1952372/20171121_Ming04_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1950000%2F1952372%2F20171121_Ming04_600.jpg&h=ae582d32&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n今次 Android 新的保安漏洞，由保安公司 MWR InfoSecurity 發現，11 月中正式向外公布，受影響的用戶主要至《Android 5.0》至《Android 7.1》的用戶，遍及手機及平板電腦等 Android 裝置。若以 Google Dashboard 官方資料顯示 (11 月 9 日為例)，使用《Android 5.0》至《Android 7.1》的用戶達 78.7% (MWR InfoSecurity 則使用 10 月 2 日的數據，因此受影響用戶為 77.8%)，意味這近八成的 Android 用戶，有機會被駭客利用該 Android 安全漏洞，向有關用戶發動攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1950000/1952372/20171121_Ming02_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1950000%2F1952372%2F20171121_Ming02_600.jpg&h=416588d2&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"3e5d3e3f5154d0d95ee7e8ece647a247766b5aee","tid":482201,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T03:06:05.000Z","msg":"今次《Android》新的保安漏洞來自《Android 5.0》版本以後，向 Android App 開發人員開放的 MediaProjection 媒體播放功能的存取權限。駭客藉此漏洞，可以不用得到用戶的授權，透過 SystemUI 自動跳出的信息提示，誘使用戶按「OK」。用戶一旦按下，駭客便可以遠端控制用戶的 Android 裝置，存取裝置內的螢幕影像內容及聲音檔案。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1950000/1952372/20171121_Ming03_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1950000%2F1952372%2F20171121_Ming03_600.jpg&h=dac0c4bd&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n那麼如何避免？從 MWR InfoSecurity 的資料顯示，由年初發現相關問題，及跟 Google 通報的 Disclosure Timeline 可見，於 2017 年 8 月，Google 已經在《Android 8.0》上修復這項漏洞。即用戶若已收到《Android 8.0》的更新推送，還是建議更新至《Android 8.0》。若未收到相關更新怎辦？也有方法可以提高免中招的機會，相關攻擊必須透過用戶按「OK」才成功，對於來歷不明的自動信息提示，不要胡亂按「OK」，必須確定相關來源，其中 MWR InfoSecurity 便示範一些例子，大家可以作為參考。"},{"pid":"d8604f8a948b1e1ecb7e7df1e27aed4a91e15c24","tid":482201,"uid":141060,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T03:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果狗早晨"},{"pid":"b2c78e46b273e1392d7e62ae11a543817646a70c","tid":482201,"uid":116530,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T03:07:19.000Z","msg":"Android狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8030e35fb1a0e7dd84dfc26352df091dbeae85a8","tid":482201,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T03:07:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果狗早晨</blockquote><br />\n三叔早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721ae77d12568e80623cb4f33cdbfe24c8aecc35","tid":482201,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T03:32:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果狗早晨</blockquote><br />\n三叔早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩個人係點係兩句對話顯示晒出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db81c92f6546d35a8867dbd21814a8a06226640e","tid":482201,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T03:44:35.000Z","msg":"Power_on都比人話果狗，真係一味屈就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45ec34be06a1df6d4bf5637ce7d3ff47d48dd121","tid":482201,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T03:55:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Power_on都比人話果狗，真係一味屈就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收皮啦你　扮乜春野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c7026ce039c87f5f812a0ba64ed82030bc4b580","tid":482201,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T03:57:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Power_on都比人話果狗，真係一味屈就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收皮啦你　扮乜春野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講野講清楚啲，power_on 不嬲係an俠。"},{"pid":"05d54d2af41e624a879bef4c67a9cbd6a1e5d103","tid":482201,"uid":44333,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T06:35:08.000Z","msg":"相關攻擊必須透過用戶按「OK」才成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f9a5ba934e21bea4eb8eeb895c4f0928ce567f","tid":482201,"uid":18127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T05:55:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b23b8a0d223fc5a6ea43524a0b5b0b2b8f982c2c","tid":482201,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:36:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>相關攻擊必須透過用戶按「OK」才成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nok 用家問題"},{"pid":"d64747e3e6086c7f4364396ef6e753a65c9745bc","tid":482201,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:07:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Android狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個名點整架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}